        img: "/images/mon-plaisir/gallery_04.webp"
      },
      {
        title: "Buitenleven",
        desc: "Het buitenleven is hier sterk aanwezig. Zonnebaad aan het zwembad, ontspan in de achtertuin of geniet van uw eigen terrasje.",
        amenities: ["Grote tuin", "Terrassen", "Zonneweide", "Rust"],
        img: "/images/mon-plaisir/gallery_07.webp"
      }
    ],
    rules: {
      title: "Goed om te weten",
      items: [
        { label: "Check-in", value: "13:00 - 22:00" },
        { label: "Check-out", value: "07:00 - 11:00" },
        { label: "Roken", value: "Alleen buiten" },
        { label: "Huisdieren", value: "Niet toegestaan" }
      ]
    }
  },
  en: {
    title: "Accommodation",
    headline: "Luxury Stay in Wolphaartsdijk",
    intro: "Step into the world of B&B Mon Plaisir. Our suites, 'Suite D’amour' and 'Suite Mon Plaisir', offer a unique combination of luxury, comfort, and peace.",
    sections: [
      {
        title: "Suite D’amour",
        desc: "A romantic suite of 20 m² on the ground floor. Enjoy your private terrace, private bathroom, and the view. Includes free WiFi and breakfast.",
        amenities: ["Private bathroom", "Private terrace", "Ground floor", "Breakfast included"],
        img: "/images/mon-plaisir/gallery_01.webp"
      },
      {
        title: "Suite Mon Plaisir",
        desc: "Our namesake: a beautiful suite of 20 m² with a view of the garden. Features a private entrance, luxury bathroom, and lovely terrace.",
