        img: "/images/mon-plaisir/gallery_03.webp"
      },
      {
        title: "Wellness & Relaxation",
        desc: "When the weather is less favorable, or just for relaxation, you can use our sauna and solarium. Outside you will find a lovely swimming pool.",
